Ah. only thing...
Sorry. have to say it.

102
00:07:41.086 --> 00:07:43.172
Uh. ladies.
do watch what you flush.

103
00:07:44.673 --> 00:07:46.008
Right. Yeah.

104
00:07:46.091 --> 00:07:48.135
